e for comfort when she wears the product.\", \"from\": 3313, \"to\": 3482, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3329, \"end\": 3337, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999996307452, \"rank\": 3.690863529872368e-10, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 3338, \"end\": 3350, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabrielle_Thomas\", \"score\": 0.9999576635281278, \"rank\": 4.233826319342971e-05, \"text\": \"Gabby Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabrielle_Thomas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabrielle_Thomas\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"similar experiences\", \"from\": 3358, \"to\": 3377}, {\"ngram\": \"the brand\", \"from\": 3383, \"to\": 3392}, {\"ngram\": \"style\", \"from\": 3437, \"to\": 3442}, {\"ngram\": \"comfort\", \"from\": 3447, \"to\": 3454}, {\"ngram\": \"the product\", \"from\": 3470, \"to\": 3481}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said in the press release: \\\"I wear a lot of loungewear when I am not competing or training but also love experimenting with fashion, so I never want to compromise on style, and Skims is the perfect balance of style and comfort!\\\"\", \"from\": 3483, \"to\": 3715, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3664, \"end\": 3669, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.651861449341724e-31, \"text\": \"Skims\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the press release\", \"from\": 3495, \"to\": 3512}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 3522, \"to\": 3527}, {\"ngram\": \"loungewear\", \"from\": 3531, \"to\": 3541}, {\"ngram\": \"fashion\", \"from\": 3611, \"to\": 3618}, {\"ngram\": \"